                <note rend="inline" type="source">891.512/–: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in Persia</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Kornfeld</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1923-07-31T17:00:00-04:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">July 31, 1923—5 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>17. Department is informed that you and other diplomatic representatives in
                    Teheran addressed a note to the Persian Government on the subject of taxation of
                    foreigners in Persia. If so telegraph date and substance of the communication
                    and mail full text immediately.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hughes</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
